====Interjection====
{{en-interj}}

# {{lb|en|slang|chiefly|Northern California}} [[for sure|For sure]]; [[totally]]; [[hell yeah]]; used as a strong affirmation of something that was just said, accomplished, or revealed.
#: ''"Hey, you wanna come to the concert tonight?" "Oh, '''helluv'''!"''

====Usage notes====
* To many speakers, ''helluv'' is the more emphatic or more intensified form of {{m|en|hella}}.

